          <div class="widget-wrap">
           <article class="post-445 page type-page status-publish entry">
            <header class="entry-header">
             <h2 class="entry-title" itemprop="headline">
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/">
               Niagara Falls  Niagara Falls Tourism Information
              </a>
             </h2>
            </header>
            <div class="entry-content">
             <p>
              Thank you for visiting Niagara Falls number one travel website and we hope you come visit soon!
             </p>
             <hr/>
             <p>
              <a href="http://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara_falls_webcam.htm">
               <img alt="" class="alignleft wp-image-10500 size-full" height="200" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/falls-webcam-opti-300x200-2.jpg" width="300"/>
              </a>
             </p>
             <p style="text-align: left;">
              The weather is beautiful and start of the prime tourism season in Niagara Falls has begun! Check out our
              <a href="http://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara_falls_webcam.htm">
               Niagara Falls Webcam
              </a>
              . It streams live 24/7 all year long. With the recent upgrade to the Falls lighting it really looks spectacular in the evenings.
              <span style="color: #ff0000;">
               SPECIAL
              </span>
              <span style="color: #ff0000;">
               NOTICE
              </span>
               The Fireworks at the Falls schedule has been updated for the 2018 season and fireworks will now be displayed every night from June 13th through September 3rd! More dates and info can be found
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara_falls_at_night.htm">
                here
               </a>
              </strong>
              .
             </p>
             <hr/>
             <h5 style="text-align: left;">
              Planning a visit?
             </h5>
             <p>
              Planning your visit to Niagara Falls has never been easier. First you need to figure out the best way to get to Niagara Falls. Our How do I get to Niagara Falls
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara_falls_transportation_links.htm">
                page
               </a>
              </strong>
              is full of information on arriving here by everything from planes to trains and automobiles. The
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara_falls_travel_tips.htm">
                Travel Tips
               </a>
              </strong>
              page offers information on crossing the border, passport information to what type of weather you can expect during your visit. Of course you will want to view the falls in all its splendor but were sure you will want to try some of the associated attractions. Just visit our
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/attractions_in_niagara_falls.htm">
                attractions
               </a>
              </strong>
              page and pick and choose what you might like to try. There are
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/discount_coupons_page_link.htm">
                discount passes
               </a>
              </strong>
              for Niagara Falls attractions available for those who want to visit multiple attractions or if you have limited time just pay as you go. The next step is to decide on where you would like to stay. Our
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara_falls_hotels.htm">
                Niagara Falls Hotels
               </a>
              </strong>
              pages offer all the insight you need to choose a place that will suit your needs. If you cant find what you are looking for check out our
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara-falls-sitemap.htm">
                sitemap
               </a>
              </strong>
              or send an email to info@niagarafallslive.com. Wed be glad to help you plan your visit!
             </p>
             <p style="text-align: center;">
              <a href="https://www.niagaracruises.com/boat-tours/?utm_source=nf-live&amp;utm_medium=banner&amp;utm_campaign=2018-mediabuy&amp;utm_content=homepage#comparison-chart" rel="noopener" target="_blank">
               <img alt="" class="aligncenter wp-image-14172 size-full" height="160" sizes="(max-width: 855px) 100vw, 855px" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/opt-hornblower-855x160-3.jpg" srcset="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/opt-hornblower-855x160-3.jpg 855w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/opt-hornblower-855x160-3-300x56.jpg 300w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/opt-hornblower-855x160-3-768x144.jpg 768w" width="855"/>
              </a>
             </p>
             <hr/>
             <p style="text-align: center;">
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara_falls_travel_tips.htm">
               <img class="alignnone wp-image-9088 size-full" height="350" sizes="(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/travel-tips-lead-in-350x350-1.jpg" srcset="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/travel-tips-lead-in-350x350-1.jpg 350w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/travel-tips-lead-in-350x350-1-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/travel-tips-lead-in-350x350-1-300x300.jpg 300w" width="350"/>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/discount_coupons_page_link.htm">
               <img class="alignnone wp-image-9064 size-full" height="350" sizes="(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-coupon-lead-in-350x350.jpg" srcset="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-coupon-lead-in-350x350.jpg 350w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-coupon-lead-in-350x350-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-coupon-lead-in-350x350-300x300.jpg 300w" width="350"/>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/map_of_the_niagara_falls_region.htm">
               <img class="alignnone wp-image-9086 size-full" height="350" sizes="(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-map-lead-in-350x350.jpg" srcset="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-map-lead-in-350x350.jpg 350w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-map-lead-in-350x350-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-map-lead-in-350x350-300x300.jpg 300w" width="350"/>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara_falls_at_night.htm">
               <img class="alignnone wp-image-9082 size-full" height="350" sizes="(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-illumination-350x350.jpg" srcset="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-illumination-350x350.jpg 350w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-illumination-350x350-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-illumination-350x350-300x300.jpg 300w" width="350"/>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/facts_about_niagara_falls.htm">
               <img class="alignnone wp-image-9068 size-full" height="350" sizes="(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-falls-facts-lead-in-350x350.jpg" srcset="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-falls-facts-lead-in-350x350.jpg 350w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-falls-facts-lead-in-350x350-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-falls-facts-lead-in-350x350-300x300.jpg 300w" width="350"/>
              </a>
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/attractions_in_niagara_falls.htm">
               <img class="alignnone wp-image-9062 size-full" height="350" sizes="(max-width: 350px) 100vw, 350px" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-attractions-lead-in-350x350.jpg" srcset="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-attractions-lead-in-350x350.jpg 350w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-attractions-lead-in-350x350-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-attractions-lead-in-350x350-300x300.jpg 300w" width="350"/>
              </a>
             </p>
             <p style="text-align: center;">
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/niagara_fallsview_waterpark_discount_coupon.htm">
               <img alt="" class="alignnone wp-image-11658 size-full" height="160" sizes="(max-width: 850px) 100vw, 850px" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-fallsview-waterpark-850x160.jpg" srcset="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-fallsview-waterpark-850x160.jpg 850w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-fallsview-waterpark-850x160-300x56.jpg 300w, https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-fallsview-waterpark-850x160-768x145.jpg 768w" width="850"/>
              </a>
             </p>
             <hr/>
             <p>
              <img alt="" class="size-full wp-image-9084 alignleft" height="173" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-jet-boat-red3001.jpg" width="300"/>
              What is the most exciting adventure besides visiting the Falls? The Whirlpool Jetboat ride is the most exhilarating ride on the planet! Over 1.5 million people have experienced the thrills of riding through the Niagara Rapids on board one of their 1200hp turbo diesel jetboats. Reservations are required and there are departures from both the Canadian and USA sides of the Niagara River. This amazing ride is considered to be one of North Americas most thrilling experiences. 2018 season begins in late April.For more information and discounted rates you can start
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/whirlpool_jetboat_tours.htm">
               <strong>
                here
               </strong>
              </a>
              .
             </p>
             <hr/>
             <p>
              <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/greg_frewin_theater_niagara_falls_canada.htm">
               <img class="alignright wp-image-9070 size-full" height="200" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-frewin-300x200.jpg" width="300"/>
              </a>
             </p>
             <p>
              <span style="line-height: 1.5em;">
               Experience the mystery and art of illusion with Greg Frewin, International Grand Champion of Magic. This Las Vegas Style Magical Review features spectacular appearances by our rare and majestic tigers. Your imagination will be captivated and you will be amazed Beyond Belief! A family friendly show featuring large cats, and illusions which astounded International audiences at the Flamingo Hilton in Las Vegas for two years. Come enjoy a Las Vegas show in Niagara Falls! For more info visit the
               <strong>
                <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/greg_frewin_theater_niagara_falls_canada.htm">
                 Greg Frewin Theatre
                </a>
               </strong>
               .
              </span>
             </p>
             <hr/>
             <p>
              If you are visiting Niagara Falls this season and would like to try something truly unique try to
              <a href="http://www.niagarafallslive.com/imax_niagara_falls.htm">
               <img alt="" class="alignright wp-image-9193 size-full" height="200" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opti-imax-300x200.jpg" width="300"/>
              </a>
              find the time to visit the IMAX Niagara Falls. This IMAX film takes an in depth look at the history surrounding our natural wonder and is something all ages can enjoy. Visit
              <strong>
               <a href="http://www.niagarafallslive.com/imax_niagara_falls.htm">
                IMAX NIAGARA FALLS
               </a>
              </strong>
              for more information!
             </p>
             <p>
             </p>
             <hr/>
             <p>
              <img class="alignleft wp-image-9861 size-full" height="200" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/optimized-hp-hiking-leadin-300x200.jpg" width="300"/>
              Many visitors to Niagara Falls are unaware that we possess some of the most beautiful hiking trails in North America. The area known as the Niagara Gorge begins at the Falls and extends almost 5.5 miles (9 km) to the north. The gorge is accessible at various points along the Niagara Parkway. You can hike down to the rivers edge for some breathtaking views of the local flora and fauna. Visit our
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/hiking_trails_niagara_falls.htm">
                hiking
               </a>
              </strong>
              page for details!
             </p>
             <p>
             </p>
             <hr/>
             <p style="text-align: left;">
              <img alt="" class="wp-image-11664 size-full alignleft" height="250" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-niagara_falls-300x250.jpg" width="300"/>
             </p>
             <p>
              Congratulations to the winners of our annual
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/photos_of_niagara_falls.htm" title="Niagara Falls Photos">
                Niagara Falls photo contest
               </a>
              </strong>
              . We had hundreds of great entries from visitors from all over the world. A big thank you to all that participated !
             </p>
             <hr/>
             <p style="text-align: left;">
              <a href="https://www.niagaratower.com/?src=nflive23aaxd21" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
               <img class="alignleft wp-image-9078 size-full" height="182" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/opt-hp-hotel-leadin-300x182.jpg" width="300"/>
              </a>
             </p>
             <p>
              Niagara Tower Hotel.
              <strong>
              </strong>
              If you are visiting Niagara Falls and want to stay at a truly unique hotel check out the Niagara Tower Hotel. Originally built in the 1960s as a restaurant and observation tower. In 2002 it was converted to a boutique hotel with floor to ceiling windows and a view that is second to none. Spend a night or two at this amazing Niagara Falls Hotel. Find more information here:
              <strong>
               <a href="https://www.niagaratower.com/?src=nflive23aaxd21" title="Niagara Tower Hotel">
                Niagara Tower Hotel
               </a>
              </strong>
              .
             </p>
             <p>
              <iframe allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" frameborder="0" height="620" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/268100802" width="100%">
               <span class="mce_SELRES_start" data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;">
                
               </span>
              </iframe>
             </p>
             <p style="text-align: left;">
              <a href="https://fallsdaysinn.com/?afflid=10003" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
               <img alt="" class="alignright wp-image-11149 size-full" height="224" src="https://www.niagarafallslive.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/08/days-inn-opti-2-290x224.jpg" width="290"/>
              </a>
             </p>
             <p style="text-align: left;">
              Stay close to the Falls for less! If you are on a budget like most of us and would like to be close to all the action at a reasonable price check out the
              <a href="https://fallsdaysinn.com/?afflid=10003" rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
               <strong>
                Days Inn Fallsview
               </strong>
              </a>
              . They have clean comfortable accommodations and the staff is great!Days Inn Fallsview features free Wi-Fi internet access in all rooms, large-vehicle parking for a nominal fee, and a refreshing seasonal outdoor pool. Jacuzzi suites are available, and kids 17 and under stay free with an adult.The Days Inn Fallsview not only offers an amazing location (1 block away from the Falls, Fallsview Casino, Niagara Parks and more) it also offers all of the amenities youd expect from a Days Inn Hotel.
             </p>
             <p>
              <iframe allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen" frameborder="0" height="620" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/244708454" width="100%">
               <span class="mce_SELRES_start" data-mce-type="bookmark" style="display: inline-block; width: 0px; overflow: hidden; line-height: 0;">
                
               </span>
              </iframe>
             </p>
             <p>
              2018 will be our twenty first year of providing the most concise information in an easy to navigate format on Niagara Falls. If you have any questions, comments or suggestions which would enhance our visitors guide feel free to contact us at
              <strong>
               info@niagarafallslive.com
              </strong>
              .
             </p>
